OL,7,FOne-way tickets to uncertainty:
OL,8,FMigrants play cat and mouse with
OL,9,Fauthorities as they try to cross from
OL,10,FItaly to France. Emma Murphy reports
OL,12,FIn Ventimiglia train station the four
OL,13,Fyoung boys heading for the train to
OL,14,FFrance all wear pristine trainers and
OL,15,Fcarry new rucksacks.
OL,17,FIn their hands they have one way
OL,18,Ftickets for the station just a few
OL,19,Fminutes away. They are almost at the
OL,20,Fplatform when an Italian soldier
OL,21,Fstops them.
OL,3,C'Pass of death': The young migrants
OL,4,Crisking it all for the chance of a
OL,5,Cnew life in France
